{"title":"asp.net后台执行js造成样式失效","date":"2011-01-12T09:49:00.000Z","slug":"asp-net后台执行js造成样式失效","updated":"2019-05-23T03:17:36.066Z","content":"<p>在asp.net中后台执行js时，比如使用Response.Write弹出一个alert</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight csharp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Response.Write(<span class=\"string\">\"&lt;script&gt;alert('确定。')&lt;/script&gt;\"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这样做有时候会造成页面的css样式表错位或者失效</p>\n<p>为了避免这样的情况，使用下面的方法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight csharp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.ClientScript.RegisterStartupScript(<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.GetType(), <span class=\"string\">\"alter\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"alert('确定。');\"</span>, <span class=\"literal\">true</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"关于数据容量","slug":"关于数据容量"},"next":{"title":"【花语】-菖蒲","slug":"cloves-changpu"},"link":"http://ojdev.github.io/post/asp-net后台执行js造成样式失效/"}